Officer Michael Slager, 33, has been charged with the murder of 50-year-old father-of-four Walter Scott in North Charleston, South Carolina .
Mr Scott was shot five times in the back as he ran from the officer's car .
The officer was allowed to stay with the force despite being subject to a complaint that alleged he used excessive force on an unarmed man .
He was allowed back with the officer despite being the subject of a complaint filed against him .